13
00:00:47,735 --> 00:00:51,535
sleep. Alpha waves dominate when you're relaxed but

14
00:00:51,535 --> 00:00:55,335
awake. Beta waves indicate active thinking and concentration.

15
00:00:55,335 --> 00:00:59,135
Gamma waves are associated with higher cognitive functions.

16
